counit_surjective:
theorem counit_surjective : surjective (counit R) :=
  acounit_surjective ℤ R
#align counit_surjective counit_surjective
counit_nat_surjective:
theorem counit_nat_surjective : surjective (counit_nat A) :=
  acounit_surjective ℕ A
#align counit_nat_surjective counit_nat_surjective
counit_nat_X:
@[simp]
theorem counit_nat_X (a : A) : counit_nat A (X a) = a :=
  acounit_X _ _
#align counit_nat_X counit_nat_X
counit_nat_C:
theorem counit_nat_C (n : ℕ) : counit_nat A (C n) = n :=
  acounit_C _ _
#align counit_nat_C counit_nat_C
counit_X:
@[simp]
theorem counit_X (r : R) : counit R (X r) = r :=
  acounit_X _ _
#align counit_X counit_X
counit_C:
theorem counit_C (n : ℤ) : counit R (C n) = n :=
  acounit_C _ _
#align counit_C counit_C
acounit_surjective:
theorem acounit_surjective : surjective (acounit A B) := fun b => ⟨X b, acounit_X A b⟩
#align acounit_surjective acounit_surjective
acounit_X:

@[simp]
theorem acounit_X (b : B) : acounit A B (X b) = b :=
  aeval_X _ b
#align acounit_X acounit_X
acounit_C:
@[simp]
theorem acounit_C (a : A) : acounit A B (C a) = algebra_map A B a :=
  aeval_C _ a
#align acounit_C acounit_C
